name: No. 33, 2016

description:
A Secret Wars chapter!

Can Mary Jane and Annie save Spider-Man from the clutches of Regent?!

Also: Can the Spiders survive long enough to stop Osborn’s crazy scheme?!!

Plus: It’s the final showdown between Spider-Man, Agent Venom, the mutated Avengers and the Queen!

By Dan Slott, Adam Kubert, Christos Gage, Paco Diaz, Mike Costa and André Lima Araújo!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man: Renew your Vows #5, Warzones: Spider-Verse #5 and Warzones: Spider-Island #5.

A Secret Wars chapter!

The wall-crawler is in deep trouble as he battles the Sinister Six and Regent!

Plus: Spider-Man, Agent Venom and the mutated Avengers take the fight to the Queen!

Also: Can Spider-Gwen save Peter Parker from Venom?!!

By Dan Slott, Adam Kubert, Christos Gage, Paco Diaz, Mike Costa and André Lima Araújo!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man: Renew your Vows #4, Warzones: Spider-Verse #4 and Warzones: Spider-Island #4.

A Secret Wars chapter!

Spidey is back in black and hunted by Regent's Sinister Six!

Also, Spider-Gwen and the Web-Warriors come face-to-face with Osborn’s Sinister Six (yes, another sextet of supervillainy)!

Plus, can Agent Venom and the Avengers rescue Spider-Man from the Queen?!

By Dan Slott, Adam Kubert, Mike Costa, André Lima Araújo, Steven Sanders, Christos Gage and Paco Diaz!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man: Renew your Vows #3, Warzones Spider-Verse #3 and Warzones: Spider-Island #3.

'The Black Vortex' saga concludes! Kitty Pryde makes a fateful choice that will decide the fate of an alien empire! By Sam Humphries, Paco Medina and Ed McGuinness!

Featuring material first printed in Legendary Star-Lord #11, Black Vortex: Omega #1 and All-New X-Men #40.
Translates Inhuman Special #1 & All-New Captain America Special #1.
Translates Free Comic Book Day 2015 (Avengers) & Uncanny Inhumans #1.
Translates Uncanny Inhumans #2, All-New All-Different Point One (All-New Inhumans) & All-New Inhumans #1.
